Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:09.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be the other you that I've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:17.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere beyond this sky is a girl with wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:21.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She spreads those wings and continues to be blown by the wind from the distant past,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:22.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,just like long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.61,0:00:28.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother passed away before she told me any more details.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:44.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, my only companions whilst traveling have been that story of the girl in the sky and this doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:49.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san, are you also searching for the same girl as your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.53,0:00:51.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's no way that you're that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:54.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Many people dream of flying through the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.38,0:00:58.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl can fly too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:00:59.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.90,0:01:00.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She has wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.86,0:01:03.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:05.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I had wings too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:00.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:02.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, freeloader, here's a present for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:06.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a sloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:10.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this cuter than that dirty doll of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:13.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I need to have you make some money so you can get out of here ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:15.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:19.84,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs54\c&HB83D41&\pos(643,96)}Episode 2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:24.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing like a drink after work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:27.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I live for these times!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:33.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, freeloader, first up tonight is touching love confessions that bring a tear to the eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:34.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Entertain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:38.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Misuzu, are you sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here. You can use my lap as a pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:46.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! I-It's okay. I'm not a child anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to bed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:51.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:54.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:01.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:03.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you let her use your lap as a pillow a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:05.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! It was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:09.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As if that girl would cuddle up to someone as pathetic as me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:13.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she say "gao" again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:16.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:18.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I whacked her each time she said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:24.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When she was little, she thought chicks were baby dinosaurs for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:30.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And so when she saw the chicks at a summer fair, she begged for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:34.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we were so poor then; we couldn't buy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:40.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, she learned to say "gao" whenever something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:43.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not cut out to be a parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:46.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have stayed alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, that girl is a little weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:52.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:56.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she seems to cheer up when she's with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:59.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so if possible, I hope you'll stay friends with her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:04.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more I can do for her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:46.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come! It's time for a fun puppet show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:05:58.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:00.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:02.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like something you might see in a dream... I mean a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:03.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on; let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:03.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:05.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me my payment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:09.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't work at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:09.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:14.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:16.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name was Potato, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:16.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikkori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:18.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:20.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko pikoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:23.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopikopiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:27.68,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko pika piko piko pika piko pikopiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:26.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:28.14,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your daughter well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:28.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:35.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She says white rice tastes great and asks for seconds and thirds, so it makes cooking worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:39.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell her to be careful of an upset stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:42.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:47.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been doing loitering in front of my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:53.64,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikapikapika piko piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go home, shall we...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.06,0:06:54.92,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't ignore me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:59.22,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko! Piko! Piko! Piko! Piko! Piiikoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Potato. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:00.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:01.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukito-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:05.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-kun is talking with Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.03,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\frz357.838\c&H0E0D0C&\pos(667,223)}KIRISHIMA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.03,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\frz357.838\c&H0E0D0C&\pos(1032,239)}CLINIC
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:10.13,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko pikopiko pi-pikopiko piko piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:12.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:15.43,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Potato's become your fan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did you say your name is Yukito Kunisaki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:24.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your skill is impressive, but I doubt you'll be able to make much money with that trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:24.01,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:24.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:25.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:31.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I've been traveling from town to town using this trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:32.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:35.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That must mean you've made lots of money in this town too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:37.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You haven't?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:45.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be interested in working at this clinic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:48.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is Hijiri Kirishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:52.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since my parents passed away, I'm the only doctor in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:55.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been looking for someone to do odd jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:57.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why bamboo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:01.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:06.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you eating nagashi soumen for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:10.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In this house, if Kano asks for nagashi soumen, we eat nagashi soumen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:12.64,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:14.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, this is an unfair seating arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:15.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:18.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd eat a lot if you didn't sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:19.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:20.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:23.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll see you tomorrow at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:25.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay me better, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:30.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, as an added benefit, I'll let you put on your puppet shows in front of my clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:34.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry; I'll let you eat lunch too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:35.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:37.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play again tomorrow, Yukito-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:38.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:41.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:43.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko! Pikooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was taking that job a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:50.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this town really doesn't have many people walking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:52.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess traffic accidents are rare too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:09:00.01,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(643,60)\fsp2.25\c&H0E0D0C&}NIINUMA  RICE  AND  LIQUOR  SHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:56.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no. It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:02.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:04.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault too for bumping into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why do you have so much stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:12.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter loves rice and eats so much of it that I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:18.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's not much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:19.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:21.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:21.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:23.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not much, but please accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:28.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't anyone in this town use actual money?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:33.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what kind of girl can eat that much rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:41.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:52.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a sloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:56.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:00.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's like a smaller version of Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:07.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what happened to your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:08.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:11.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lost by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:18.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:24.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's yummy and cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Decide whether it's yummy or cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:28.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute and yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:30.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukito-san, who is this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:37.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:37.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Six-years-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:39.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What an incredible name!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:41.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san, keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:42.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:45.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what you say before your age, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Saika Shino, six-years-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shino-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:50.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:52.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:11:00.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that girl has to be admitted to hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:01.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:02.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:05.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't seem too serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:10.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And she said the sloth has become her friend, so she'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:12.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:20.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:22.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:23.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:25.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:26.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a dream about the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:31.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:34.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a world I'd never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:40.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See, when you sit like this, the clouds are above you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:45.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But in my dream, the clouds were beneath my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:49.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Between the clouds, I could see the bright blue of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:53.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't tell how far it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:56.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything extended endlessly into infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:11:59.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:03.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,did you have wings in your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:04.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:07.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:12.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't go around telling people about such dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:27.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it fits you well somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:29.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a different one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:32.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest are all too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:35.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, it smells nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:40.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:41.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A boxed lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:44.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I put all my effort into it, so it's exceedingly delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:45.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A boxed lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:49.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You went to the trouble just for...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:51.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please deliver it to Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:52.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:56.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano is at school again taking care of the animals today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:13:00.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you dare eat it on the way there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:02.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it carefully and quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:08.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we stop by the bookstore?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are quite a lot of students.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:12.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they're here for remedial classes, club activities, or student government.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:13.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:18.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be a good place to set up shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:17.36,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:21.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please welcome my puppet show with lots of applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.53,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&HDEDEDE&\move(523,97,543,132,0,2692)}YUKITO
