Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.53,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&H7E7468&\frz20.715\move(49,544,123,524,22,2692)}KUNI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.53,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&H7E7468&\frz340.085\move(211,535,262,516,22,2692)}SAKI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:27.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki, you're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki, you're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Love and Peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:31.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki, you're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that'll ever happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:33.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:35.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:35.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:40.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I take this weird creature in, the high school might erupt in a great panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move from here until I tell you it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:46.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:49.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I'd like to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:50.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:53.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to deliver a boxed lunch to Kano Kirishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:54.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:55.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano-rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano-rin... Maybe she's still in the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:01.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:04.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going to the rooftop because she wanted some air.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:08.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said, "kyuu," and collapsed all of a sudden after mumbling something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:10.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she just got a little light-headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:19.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:21.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:25.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:28.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt a little dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:30.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:32.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky is so high, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:36.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-kun, can't you fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can move a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:40.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That has absolutely nothing to do with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:48.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, didn't you say something about if you could use magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:49.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:51.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because I can use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:52.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:53.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not completely true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:55.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use it until I grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:59.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've already decided what I'll do with my first spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:01.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:02.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you what I'll do second, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:06.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't particularly want to hear about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:07.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:10.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't listen, it'll claw its way out of your stomach
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:14.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and turn into something so strong that mankind can't even fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:16.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Earth, the Earth is in great trouble!" Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:16.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:18.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to protect the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:20.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the second thing you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:22.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to fly through the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:30.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic to fly through the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:31.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:34.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:38.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't attack me so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:39.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:42.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And after I went through the trouble of calling out to you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:43.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:46.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My head is spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:49.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a dirty doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:50.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:51.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so tattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:55.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're suffering under a stupid master, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:56.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that so poignantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:58.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:15:59.22,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:00.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:01.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:07.69,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&HF3F3F3&\pos(679,126)\frz359.5}SHIMANO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:07.69,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(863,129)\frz359.216\c&HF3F3F3&}BOOKSTORE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:07.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a Butt Swayling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:10.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:17.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:18.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:19.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Minagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:33.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:36.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You get to have Minagi fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:38.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:39.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you to act so high and mighty?!
Comment: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:39.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,ALTERNATIVE: Who are you to tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:40.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:41.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:44.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's all nice now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:44.18,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... you're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:45.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:48.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a very precious doll to you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,since you are always carrying it around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:52.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the physical form of a precious memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:56.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:58.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:00.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:03.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that might be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:06.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You ruined the mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:07.36,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:12.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I present you with a coupon for rice.
