Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:13.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:16.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Tohno-san great?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:31.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only is she good at her studies, but she's good at sewing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:32.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:34.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:36.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A place where lots of people gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:41.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put on your puppet show there, you'll have many customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:42.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:44.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:47.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what kind of work does she do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:48.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:51.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she went to pray at the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:52.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:54.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's where we're headed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:17:58.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for the summer festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:02.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be full of people then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:05.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of kids from town will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:09.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids in this town are all unruly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:11.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Waah, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:12.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:14.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:18.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're here, I thought we could play some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:20.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play hide-and-seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:21.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:22.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide-and-seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:24.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How old do you think we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:28.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Then... let's catch bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:30.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gao~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:40.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:42.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:46.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care what we play, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:49.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer vacation, so I want to play as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:55.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:59.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going now, got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:01.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:04.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:26.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it, do you still believe that when a chick grows up, it'll become a dinosaur?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:28.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Geez, I know already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:31.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chicks grow up to be chickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:38.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, what I really wanted wasn't a chick or a baby dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:42.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I heard that you cried all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:47.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It didn't matter what it was, as long as Mommy bought it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:54.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fun day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:55.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:56.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:20:00.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had so much fun on my birthday before, so I'm really glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:03.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's... your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:04.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:08.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you keep quiet about something that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:09.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:12.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd known, I would've tried to buy you a present at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:12.27,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27\frz343.316\pos(853,734)}Rice\NCoupon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:12.44,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27\frz342.809\pos(810,571)}Rice\NCoupon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:12.56,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27\frz344.93\pos(783,492)}Rice\NCoupon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.52,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27\frz343.578\pos(769,450)}Rice\NCoupon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:15.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:16.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:26.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one would watch a puppet show at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:28.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you done for the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.77,0:20:29.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:31.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me something, even if it's just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:39.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:41.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:45.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't suppose kids would be interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:47.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.30,0:20:51.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:53.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to visit some friends, but they weren't home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:55.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A thank-you gift for showing me something so unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:09.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you lucky that I was given a cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:13.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, and the number of candles was just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:17.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he was planning to celebrate someone's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:21.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Haruko remember that today is your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:23.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy's busy, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.01,0:21:35.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:37.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:38.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:44.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:45.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:46.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:51.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The shrine again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:53.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she went in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:54.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:58.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the number of stars in the heavens,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:02.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the number of trees in the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.45,0:22:03.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the number...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.56,0:22:05.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:43.81,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fad(400,900)\fs51\shad2.25\pos(641,293)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:43.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least work enough to earn your wages.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:44.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.45,0:23:46.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.06,0:23:48.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:49.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.01,0:23:52.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.51,0:23:55.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many mysteries in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.04,0:23:57.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she always weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:23:58.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.11,0:24:01.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if there's nothing, then it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.90,0:24:02.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.16,0:24:04.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.73,0:24:04.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.59,0:24:06.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.13,0:24:09.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it well at all!
