Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.38,0:02:24.47,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}Chasing, chasing the fading vapor trails
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.34,0:02:32.12,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}It hasn't changed since the day we crossed that hill
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.12,0:02:34.38,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}And never will
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.45,0:02:40.52,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}And just as we are now, standing tall
